PortGroup           github 1.0

github.setup        facebook rocksdb 5.7.2 rocksdb-

revision            0
categories          databases devel
platforms           darwin
license             BSD

maintainers         stromnov openmaintainer

description         Embedded key-value store for fast storage
long_description    ${description}

homepage            http://rocksdb.org/

checksums           rmd160  78284cbbecc6817869c8fc800588985929f643dc \
                    sha256  6a53a4aee8e1dfc199b21087563360e1cf3dccfb902a353924275151df633859

